### Send message
POST http://localhost:4000/api/conversations/14155552671/messages
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: changeme

{
  "text": "Hello from REST Client!",
  "meta_msg_id": "meta_123"
}

### Update status
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/messages/wamid.1/status
